        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1800
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "バルゴさん、足止めありがとうございました！\nさくら達に無事伝えて……ってあれ、バルゴさん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Barugo-san‚ thanks for holding them off!\nI managed to pass the message to Sakura and the others… huh? Barugo-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6333334048,
      "endTime": 11.0395917971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！　バルゴが心配ゲシか？\n……見るゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geshi geshi geshi! Worried about Barugo‚ are you‚ geshi?\n…Take a look‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2462586164,
      "endTime": 17.1862596749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ば、バルゴさん！？　ぐ、ぐったりしている……\nまさかバルゴさんにてるてる坊主の刑を！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-Barugo-san!? She… she’s completely exhausted…\nDon’t tell me you gave Barugo-san the “teru-teru bozu” punishment!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3795929033,
      "endTime": 24.912835415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "仲間を裏切る方が悪いっしょ～？\nウチらはバルゴっちのこと信じてたんだしさ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Betraying your buddies is worse‚ don’t you think~?\nWe trusted Barugo-chi‚ you know~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0995019673,
      "endTime": 32.0061656712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達にヒントを伝えたようやけど……\nもう時空の狭間が閉じるのも時間の問題や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like you passed the hint to Sakura and the others…\nbut it’s only a matter of time before the rift closes now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1994990427,
      "endTime": 40.1528350908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どんなに急いでもあの距離からこの世界までは\n10分以上かかる……フッ。無念だね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how fast they hurry‚ it’ll take more than ten minutes\nto get to this world from that distance… Hmph. What a pity…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3661682526,
      "endTime": 50.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "邪魔者も消えて、これで本当にこっちの世界の\nBIG4は私達になるゲシ！　ゲーシゲシゲシゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that the nuisances are gone‚ we’ll finally become\nthis world’s BIG 4‚ geshi! Gee-shi geshi geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2328346649,
      "endTime": 59.9661699691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうゲシ！　いいことを思いついたゲシ！\n記念に今からゲリラライブを開催するゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yes‚ geshi! I’ve thought of something great!\nTo celebrate‚ we’ll hold a guerrilla live concert right now‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1661697784,
      "endTime": 67.6928324142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ゲリラライブ……！？　何言ってるんだ！\n今から会場なんて押さえられないぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A guerrilla live concert…!? What are you talking about!?\nThere’s no way you can secure a venue now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8994990426,
      "endTime": 73.2922429162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "もっと頭を使えゲシ！　お前達にとってはただの\n机でも……私達にとっては広大なステージゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Use your brain more‚ geshi! What looks like just a\ndesk to you… is a vast stage to us‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4855762877,
      "endTime": 83.0455746092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "スマホで配信の準備をするゲシ！\nさぁ……最高のショーの始まりゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Prepare the livestream on the smartphone‚ geshi!\nNow then… the greatest show begins‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2522414284,
      "endTime": 91.965575798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！　ゲーシゲシゲシ！\n……ん！？　な、何ゲシか、この光は……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gee-shi geshi geshi! Gee-shi geshi geshi!\n…Huh!? Wh-what is this light‚ geshi…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1522424457,
      "endTime": 101.95224874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_vanish-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_teleportation-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10000.002225300008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うわぁぁぁぁぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaaaaaah…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0189238625,
      "endTime": 105.1820003429,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4662.939294200001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3429.7290962999937
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "マ！？　さくら達がこっちの世界に！？\n理解不能なんですけど～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way!? Sakura and the others are in this world!?\nI can’t wrap my head around this~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2818621394,
      "endTime": 112.0885340449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "川咲さくら、完全復活！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kawasaku Sakura‚ fully revived!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2818672256,
      "endTime": 115.91531962549999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はっ……！　あなた達がザグラちゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…! You’re Zagura-chan and the others!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9153196255,
      "endTime": 119.1595306472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いたっ！　な、何か踏んづけてしまいましたわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ouch! I-I think I stepped on something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3595308379,
      "endTime": 123.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大変ですわ、これは小さい方の私！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my… this is the small version of me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.8333333333,
      "endTime": 129.8424465256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zuzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ギュエーー！！\nキュルルルル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyeeeeh!!\nKyururururu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0424466209,
      "endTime": 133.6091030196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お前がガナか！　kanaをよくもこんな目にあわせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re Gana! How dare you do this to kana!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.809103115,
      "endTime": 137.9982252359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "くれたなぁ！？　こうしてやる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Take this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9982252359,
      "endTime": 140.0648837645,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_poi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.666666700002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.333333299993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "speakerNameEn": "gana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "きゃー！　で、デコピンで飛ばさないでぇ～～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! D-don’t flick me away with a finger~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0702287751,
      "endTime": 144.2168912965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら！　みんな……！\nやっと帰って来れたんだな……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura! Everyone…!\nYou finally made it back…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4035580395,
      "endTime": 149.3103609799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待った！　さっきから好き勝手やって\nくれとんなぁ！？　あぁ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold it right there! You’ve been doing whatever you want\nthis whole time‚ huh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5036942083,
      "endTime": 155.0970348913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ええい、面倒くさいゲシ！\n誰かあいつらをやっつけてしまうゲシ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ this is annoying‚ geshi!\nSomeone just get rid of them‚ geshi~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3037013291,
      "endTime": 161.4436709642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6427.99340900001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_06-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……待つんだザグラ！　こんなことはもうやめろ！\nSMALL4を目指していた\n昔の自分を思い出せエイヨー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ Zagura! Stop this already!\nRemember when we aimed\nto become the SMALL4—remember your old self‚ AYO!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6370041449,
      "endTime": 171.0349790493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
